casebody.data:
Perry ROUHANI, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
SUPERIOR FENCE & RAIL OF PINELLAS COUNTY, INC., et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D16-4325 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. April 16, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This is an appeal from an order entered in the proceedings supplementary to a final judgment entered in lower court case number 2009-CA-007533. That final judgment has been reversed by this court. 1385 Starkey, LLC v. Superior Fence & Rail of Pinellas County. Inc., 44 Fla. L. Weekly D251 (Fla. 2d DCA Jan. 18, 2019). As a result, this appeal is dismissed as moot.

NORTHCUTT, VILLANTI, and BLACK, JJ., Concur.
